Package: inrep
Type: Package
Title: Instant Reports for Adaptive Assessments
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-07-20
Authors@R: person("Clievins", "Selva", 
                  email = "selva@uni-hildesheim.de", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9980-7127"))
Description: A comprehensive framework for adaptive testing using Item Response Theory 
    (IRT) models. Provides web-based interfaces for test administration via 'Shiny', 
    supports multiple IRT models including the Graded Response Model through 'TAM' 
    integration, implements adaptive item selection algorithms, includes LLM integration 
    for enhanced user assistance and study configuration, website theme scraping for 
    automatic branding, and comprehensive reporting capabilities. Designed for 
    psychological assessments, educational testing, and survey research with large item pools.
URL: https://github.com/selvastics/inrep
BugReports: https://github.com/selvastics/inrep/issues
